# Trocado / Cordato — Budgets
# uv run poe serve   →   uvicorn em 127.0.0.1:8000, hot-reload
# Swagger UI: http://127.0.0.1:8000/schema/swagger
#
# Obtenha um token via http/authentication.http e cole em @token abaixo.

@host = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@token = <paste-token-here>

### Criar orçamento (com nota) → 201 Created
POST {{host}}/v1/budgets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": "500.00",
  "start_date": "2026-06-01",
  "end_date": "2026-06-30",
  "note": "mercado"
}

### Criar orçamento (sem nota — campo opcional) → 201 Created
POST {{host}}/v1/budgets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": "1200.00",
  "start_date": "2026-07-01",
  "end_date": "2026-07-31"
}

### Criar orçamento com período sobreposto → 409 Conflict
POST {{host}}/v1/budgets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": "300.00",
  "start_date": "2026-06-15",
  "end_date": "2026-07-15"
}

### Criar orçamento sem autenticação → 401 Unauthorized
POST {{host}}/v1/budgets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": "500.00",
  "start_date": "2026-08-01",
  "end_date": "2026-08-31"
}
